<mxCell id="leg" value="Dependency Rule (Clean Architecture p.8):&#10;source-code dependencies point only inward.&#10;&#10;Inner = abstract, general, rarely change (Entities).&#10;Outer = concrete, specific, change frequently&#10;(Frameworks &amp; Drivers).&#10;&#10;If an inner layer seems to need an outer one:&#10;invert the dependency — declare an interface&#10;(Boundary) in the inner layer, implement it in&#10;the outer layer (DIP)." style="rounded=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;align=left;verticalAlign=top;spacing=8;fillColor=#fff2cc;strokeColor=#d6b656;" vertex="1" parent="1"><mxGeometry x="800" y="150" width="340" height="230" as="geometry"/></mxCell>
<mxCell id="e1" value="dependencies point inward" style="edgeStyle=none;rounded=0;html=1;strokeWidth=2;exitX=0;exitY=0.5;exitDx=0;exitDy=0;entryX=0;entryY=0.5;entryDx=0;entryDy=0;" edge="1" parent="1" source="r1" target="r4"><mxGeometry relative="1" as="geometry"/></mxCell>
